data.description: Old Town Charm in Elgin. Only 14 miles to the new Samsung plant in Taylor, and 17 miles to the Tesla plant.  Curb appeal as you walk up to the property, mature tress and a back yard with a large shed with the possibility of turning it into an additional living quarters.  Waking distance to surrounding restaurants, schools and historic Elgin memorial park.  New roof in 2020, new A/C in 2020. Upgrades includes appliances, granite counter tops, new cabinets, luxury vinyl laminate floors.
